# AWP + Cursor (router)

- **Design docs (human-accessible):** `docs/` — use `@docs/` in prompts. Specs, ADRs, product vision.
- **Execution registers:** `.awp-workspace/workspace-build/*.yaml` — queue, readiness, traceability. Edit YAML only; hooks run `make awp-render`.

Full contract: `.awp-workspace/workspace-build/AGENTS.md`. Phase rules: `awp-design.mdc`, `awp-build.mdc`, `awp-verify.mdc`. Build loop: `docs/design/build-agent-loop.md`. Token/model tier: repo root `AGENTS.md`.

## Session start

1. Read `.awp-workspace/workspace-build/2-build/WORK_QUEUE.yaml` + matching `1-design/TASK_READINESS.yaml`
2. Read task `spec_link` under `docs/` (often `docs/product/project-brief.md` or `docs/design/features/`)
3. For backend code: `backend/AGENTS.md`

## Commands

```bash
make awp-render
make awp-docs-check
make awp-workflow-status
make awp-install-hooks   # git pre-commit
```

Hooks in `.cursor/hooks.json` auto-render after register YAML edits.
